# MKSAP Scraper - Environment Variables

# ============================================
# API Key (OPTIONAL - for fallback only)
# ============================================
#
# By default, the scraper uses Claude Code CLI (headless mode) which:
# - Uses your Claude Code IDE subscription
# - NO API KEY REQUIRED
# - Free (no external costs)
#
# This API key is ONLY used as a fallback when:
# 1. Claude Code daily usage limit is reached
# 2. Claude Code CLI is unavailable
#
# To enable API key fallback, uncomment and set:
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...
#
# Get your API key from: https://console.anthropic.com/
#
# ============================================
# Cost Estimate (if using API key fallback):
# - ~$0.01-0.02 per error diagnosis
# - ~$0.005-0.01 per question (assuming 5-10% error rate)
# - Total: ~$10-20 for 2000 questions
# ============================================
